&lt;h3 id="2-generate-sources-listsh--tạo-file">2. &lt;code>generate-sources-list.sh&lt;/code> – &lt;strong>Tạo file &lt;code>sources.list&lt;/code> cho client&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h3>&lt;h4 id="-nhiệm-vụ-1">✅ Nhiệm vụ:
&lt;/h4>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Duyệt file &lt;code>conf/distributions&lt;/code> để lấy danh sách các &lt;code>Codename&lt;/code> và &lt;code>Component&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Sinh ra dòng cấu hình repo chuẩn cho &lt;code>apt&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h4 id="-nội-dung-chính-1">🧩 Nội dung chính:
&lt;/h4>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
